message: Added jest as launch target to be able to debug tests.
Removed console.log and reformatted, upped version number to prepare for new package.
Removed redundant code after testing with mathjs.

Removed use of mathjs

MathJS depended on a few other libraries, one of them, escape-latex, had an issue with some config data in package.json that raised some errors when adding the react-navigation-fluid-transitions package. Tried to remove use of MathJS and use regular Javascript trig, and it worked. Backed by our tests.
Move prop-types to dep. + fix lodash imports
Updated project with latest dependencies and simpler directory structure.
WIP: Working on a correct set of dependencies for RN 0.56.0 and Babel 7

Updated with support for react-native-screens

- Use useScreens() in your startup code.

Updated with react-navigation-stack and gesture handlers

- Added correct imports
- Fixed example code
- Added defaultNavigationOptions
